import React from 'react' import Field from './Field' import './Home.css' import Fielddetails from './Fielddetails' function Home() { const [data, setData] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { const sendingPost = { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: '{"query": "{allPersons{name, wins,loses}}"}' }; fetch('http://127.0.0.1:8000/graphql/', sendingPost) .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => setData(data.data.allPersons)); },[]) return (
) } export default Home
